On Mon, 25 Jul 2005, MissVeeDub wrote:

> I have heard of newer cars, when you reverse with the e-brake on it actually
> tightens the e-brake. I don't believe the buses ever came with this
> option....

Bay-window buses did not, but this is exactly how the adjusters on
Vanagons work (and the adjusters on just about every other car in
creation)

BTW, the backing plate and adjuster mechanism from a vanagon will fit on a
bay.  It isn't easy but it is possible.

